metadata.name: Lucky Guzman - Hit The Lights
metadata.description:
'Hit The Lights' is the second track from the Geek Squad Guzman EP.  
This will debut on the blockchain before migrating to all DSPs.  
A collection of 7 unique 1/1 ETH Music NFTs.  
Includes 5 GSG Passes, that serve as an entry pass into a token-gated website with exclusive content like BTS footage of the EP making process.  
A private Video chat link for open line of communication.  
25% off all Geek Squad Guzman Collection NFTs.  
Owners will receive 1 music video NFT once the EP has been fully minted.(7 records)
